{"tid":1744610,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"政府拆咗好多連儂牆","createTime":"2019-11-21T23:43:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T01:43:47.000Z","uid":76710,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"af8622a5979b0c4cc218c13f0f873159983e20ee","tid":1744610,"uid":76710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T23:43:53.000Z","msg":"其實點解政府要拆連儂牆?<br />\n好簡單: <br />\n1. 湊你PolyU大敗之後再挫你士氣<br />\n對於前線就根本唔會理你牆務係點，<br />\n但對於拆牆就特別對和理非最有用。<br />\n<br />\n2. 俾自私豬、藍絲一個信息，我地打羸杖<br />\n自私豬最想求穩定，而藍絲就係想報仇。<br />\n而家政府拆左你牆就係想自私豬、藍絲覺得政府做到野，<br />\n覺得支持政府、建制有薯數。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以而家做嘅係，叫班和理非唔好再咁戇鳩，<br />\n咪撚再同人或者網上講「我好嬲」、「我好想喊」、「見到前線俾人拉又做唔到野」，<br />\n再重申呢場運動係要大家做野，唔係網上打飛機、罵情緒同埋口號式抗爭，<br />\n講過「撕一貼十」、「香港人報仇」、「和武合一」就要用行動去做，<br />\n如果唔係就返大灣區再教育。<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命。"},{"pid":"001f2544ca429a2fa0fb942d0b304909bb585083","tid":1744610,"uid":307619,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T23:46:10.000Z","msg":"高質Po<br />\n就算推唔郁都留個言"},{"pid":"7ea9c1154b7c94ccf60c207140afed77cc0b0f08","tid":1744610,"uid":76710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"001f2544ca429a2fa0fb942d0b304909bb585083","tid":1744610,"uid":307619,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T23:46:10.000Z","msg":"高質Po<br />\n就算推唔郁都留個言"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T00:01:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"86f3c069a01daa883bc338a2018a898d57c4feaa","tid":1744610,"uid":58608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T00:03:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"134d4d9f5121d2909ee10165167fa256c34a3eae","tid":1744610,"uid":86833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T00:05:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1263874121844345e9ea33d2f55aea66b4a3da9c","tid":1744610,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T00:06:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70bbb21a527054dc2784f9ce2a5cb39103aab6f0","tid":1744610,"uid":256